data.description: Spacious two-story home in Lafayette is ready for you to move in. Conveniently located in the heart of wine country. Enjoy two separate living areas on the main level and a large fenced backyard. This layout features an upstairs laundry room to keep chores easy and plenty of storage throughout. The primary suite is located on the upper level and has two walk-in closets.
